OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1961FCoronation Street begins airing
OL,7,Fon Mondays and Wednesday at 7.30pm.
OL,8,FPreviously, it was broadcast at 7pm on
OL,9,FWednesdays and Fridays.
OL,10,
OL,11,CG1964FThe first edition of Vision On
OL,12,Fairs on BBC TV.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG1976FThe first edition of Saturday
OL,15,FNight at the Mill airs on BBC One.
OL,16,
OL,17,CG1982FThe final episode of Dick Turpin
OL,18,Fairs on ITV.
OL,19,
OL,20,CG1990FThe first episode of Chancer
OL,21,Fairs on ITV.
