OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1993FNoel's House Party (BBC One) is
OL,7,Fcancelled due to a bomb scare at BBC
OL,8,FTelevision Centre. The show is replaced
OL,9,Fby a repeat of the 1991 edition of
OL,10,FNoel's Christmas Presents, followed by
OL,11,Fa Tom and Jerry cartoon. Noel appeared
OL,12,Flive from NC1 Con/CBBC Broom Cupboard
OL,13,Fto link the replacement programmes.
OL,14,
OL,15,CG1994FThe final episode of The House
OL,16,Fof Eliott airs on BBC One. Created by
OL,17,FEileen Atkins and Jean Marsh. Starring
OL,18,FStella Gonet, Louise Lombard and Aiden
OL,19,FGillett.
